=Description=

"THE ULTIMATE OBJECTIVE OF THIS PROJECT, The Coalescence [http://www.thecoalescence.net/], is to design an ecologically and environmentally sustainable economic system that is capable of providing every individual on the planet with all of life's essentials (Air, Water, Food, Clothing, Shelter, Information, Communication, Transportation, Health Care, and Energy), and to do it in a way so convincingly that it will contribute to the advancement of the coming global coalescence, resulting in the transformation of seven billion individuals into a single harmonious social organism."


